            "text": "RTB · 2A DAILY INTEL · Friday, July 24, 2026",
            "spacing": "None"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Large",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "text": "Three circuits, three answers in a single month: the First Circuit’s ruling upholding Massachusetts’ AR-15 ban completes the appellate split the Supreme Court will resolve this fall — and DOJ has opened a second front in the Virgin Islands.",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "A unanimous First Circuit upheld Massachusetts’ AR-15 ban (Recchia v. Campbell, 7/21) — the third appellate ‘assault weapon’ ruling this month, after the 3rd Circuit struck New Jersey’s and the 7th upheld Illinois’. It completes the split SCOTUS resolves in Viramontes this fall.",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "color": "Warning",
            "text": "HOTTEST LEADS",
            "spacing": "Medium"
          },
          {
            "type": "FactSet",
            "facts": [
              {
                "title": "1. First Circuit upholds Massachusetts AR-15 ban",
                "value": "Heat 86 ▲▲"
              },
              {
                "title": "2. New Jersey — T-7 to July 31 effective date",
                "value": "Heat 83 ▲"
              },
              {
                "title": "3. Virginia — sales confirmed live (PSA)",
                "value": "Heat 74 →"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "color": "Warning",
            "text": "WHAT’S MOVING",
            "spacing": "Medium"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "wrap": true,
            "text": "• 1st Cir. upholds Massachusetts’ AR-15 ban (Recchia, 7/21)\n• DOJ moves to block USVI Act 9113 — hearing Aug 19\n• Virginia sales confirmed live — PSA resumes shipments\n• New Jersey T-7 to the July 31 effective date"
